caption.p: Anti-cancer mechanism of Tualang, Gelam and Kelulut honeys. KRAS: K-Ras encoding gene; ERK: extracellular signal-regulated kinase; AKT: protein kinase B; Bcl-xL: B-cell lymphoma-extra-large; NF-kB: nuclear factor kappa B; TWIST1: Twist-related protein 1 gene; RAC1: Ras-related C3 botulinum toxin substrate 1 gene; CCND1: Cyclin D1 gene; EGFR: epidermal growth factor receptor gene; COX-2: cyclooxygenase-2.
